ğŸ§ª Example Walkthrough
For input: s = "{[()]}"

{ â†’ push â†’ stack = [{]

[ â†’ push â†’ stack = [{, []

( â†’ push â†’ stack = [{, [, (]

) â†’ matches ( â†’ pop â†’ stack = [{, []

] â†’ matches [ â†’ pop â†’ stack = [{]

} â†’ matches { â†’ pop â†’ stack = []

Stack is empty â†’ âœ… Valid! 
